channel.title: How to edit server host?
channel.description:
Okay so I wanted to know how exactly I can change the server I downloaded's IP location and No-IP host thingy, I can't figure out how to do this or atleast change the server so it's default offline server for now because I can't even log into it, so I just want to log into it without going online for now. So the server I have is a 614 and it's client is a 562 I think and it has no client.jar it just has clientlibs.jar, the client starts with a .exe application.
This is the server I downloaded, it is not a virus, it's an application installer and a virus/keylogger wouldn't be a normal 508-614 server size of around 130mb - http://megaupload.com/?d=5YR7IXSY
Please anybody?
